This is a missed-optimization in LazyValueInfo.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i1 @binop_eval_order(i32 %x) {
  %a = add nuw nsw i32 %x, 1
  %b = add nuw nsw i32 %a, 1
  %c = add nuw nsw i32 %a, %b
  %d = icmp ugt i32 %c, 2
  ret i1 %d
}

```

